### Quota GraphQL Operations
### Uses test subscriber IDs from db/seeds/000001_test_data.up.sql
### Active subscribers:
###   cb2fec7d-1035-40f1-8d62-d3fbddfb6dc2  MSISDN: 0272587305
###   e439cec6-a092-465e-89b7-d986a536ea90  MSISDN: 0271234567

### 1. quotaBalance — balance for a specific subscriber and unit type
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/charging/graphql
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

{
  "query": "query QuotaBalance($req: QuotaBalanceRequestInput!) { quotaBalance(balanceEnquiryRequest: $req) { unitType totalValue availableBalance } }",
  "variables": {
    "req": {
      "subscriberId": "cb2fec7d-1035-40f1-8d62-d3fbddfb6dc2",
      "unitType": "OCTETS",
      "balanceType": "AVAILABLE_BALANCE"
    }
  }
}

### 2. quotaBalance — monetary balance
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/charging/graphql
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

{
  "query": "query QuotaBalance($req: QuotaBalanceRequestInput!) { quotaBalance(balanceEnquiryRequest: $req) { unitType totalValue availableBalance } }",
